OL,3,CPrincess of Wales lays wreath at
OL,4,CCenotaph to mark Anzac day
OL,6,FThe Princess of Wales has honoured
OL,7,FCommonwealth soldiers as she laid a
OL,8,Fwreath at the Cenotaph in London to
OL,9,Fmark Anzac Day.
OL,11,FHundreds of people pressed against a
OL,12,Ffence to watch as Kate commemorated
OL,13,Flanding of troops of the Australian
OL,14,Fand New Zealand Army Corps ` shortened
OL,15,Fto Anzac ` on the western shore of the
OL,16,FGallipoli peninsula on April 25 1915.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
