OL,3,CPrincess of Wales lays wreath at
OL,4,CCenotaph to mark Anzac day
OL,6,FThe Gallipoli campaign, part of a
OL,7,FBritish-led effort to defeat the
OL,8,FOttoman Empire, aimed to secure a
OL,9,Fnaval route through the Dardanelles
OL,10,Ffrom the Mediterranean Sea to
OL,11,FConstantinople, now Istanbul, in
OL,12,FTurkey. M
OL,14,FMore than 100,000 troops died in the
OL,15,Ffailed campaign that lasted into 1916.
OL,17,FA female sailor in New Zealand naval
OL,18,Funiform handed the princess a wreath,
OL,19,Fwhich she placed at the foot of the
OL,20,Fnational war memorial on Whitehall.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
