PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777277174
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales lays wreath at
OL,4,CCenotaph to mark Anzac day
OL,6,FThe ring of poppies with white flowers
OL,7,Fdepicting the feathers of the Prince
OL,8,Fof Wales' crest had a note signed by
OL,9,FCatherine and William that read: "In
OL,10,Fmemory of the Australian and New
OL,11,FZealand soldiers who made the ultimate
OL,12,Fsacrifice for our freedom."
OL,14,FThe high commissioners for New Zealand
OL,15,Fand Australia, Hamish Cooper and Jay
OL,16,FWeatherill, then walked in tandem to
OL,17,Flay their wreaths.
OL,26,@qD@bOUtD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
