PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777277174
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales lays wreath at
OL,4,CCenotaph to mark Anzac day
OL,6,F"We cannot gather on this day
OL,7,Fremembering the sacrifice of the
OL,8,FAnzacs, and all those who have served
OL,9,Fus and given their lives in pursuit of
OL,10,Fpeace, without allowing their legacy
OL,11,Fto challenge us once again.
OL,13,F"For as today we honour the courage
OL,14,Fand as we give thanks and pray for
OL,15,Fthose in active service, so we too
OL,16,Fmust choose to be people of courage as
OL,17,Fwe go from this place today, in our
OL,18,Fcommunities to be those who choose a
OL,19,Fpath that leads away from destruction
OL,20,Fand toward life."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU|D@QO]
