OL,3,CPrincess of Wales lays wreath at
OL,4,CCenotaph to mark Anzac day
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FEarlier on Saturday, the Princess
OL,12,FRoyal attended a dawn service at
OL,13,FWellington Arch at Hyde Park Corner in
OL,14,FLondon.
OL,16,FOrganised by the New Zealand and
OL,17,FAustralian high commissions, Anne
OL,18,Farrived for the Anzac service shortly
OL,19,Fbefore it started at 5am.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
