PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777277174
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales lays wreath at
OL,4,CCenotaph to mark Anzac day
OL,6,FShe laid a wreath against Wellington
OL,7,FArch during a service that included a
OL,8,Freading of the John McCrae poem In
OL,9,FFlanders Fields and concluded with the
OL,10,Fnational anthems of the United
OL,11,FKingdom, New Zealand and Australia.
OL,13,FServices were also held across New
OL,14,FZealand, Australia and on the
OL,15,FGallipoli peninsula in Turkey on
OL,16,FSaturday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
